JINR-      Joint Inst. for Nucl. Res., Dubna, reports      4ZZZDUB9000100600892 
            Note: the 4-digits report number is unique, the       9000100600893 
             symbols between JINR and number can be omitted.      9000100600894 
             They mean P=Russian, E=English, D=Engl+Russian.      9000100600895 
             The digit following this character denotes the       9000100600896 
             subject category, e.g.                               9000100600897 
               3 = low-energy experimental physics                9000100600898 
               4 = low-energy theoretical physics                 9000100600899 
              15 = exp'tl phys.of nucl.reactions at low en.       9000100600900
